    "102920": {
        "Desc": "Talk to everyone",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Arataki Itto",
                    "T": "Ushi, you sure you can't find a way back to that door again?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Ushi",
                    "T": "Moo..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "About the door..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Arataki Itto",
                    "T": "Ah, perfect timing! I was just having a chat with Ushi about that!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Arataki Itto",
                    "T": "You know what? I can handle those mean people behind the door throwing beans at me. But causing trouble for you? Nah-uh, that ain't gonna fly with this guy!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Ushi",
                    "T": "Moo..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Arataki Itto",
                    "T": "What? There's nothing we can do? Listen here, Beefcake, you shouldn't give up so easily."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Arataki Itto",
                    "T": "Can't you have one last look for it? If you really can't find it, we'll just have to find another door. With any luck, one that connects to the outside world. You feel me?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "What do we do from here..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Arataki Itto",
                    "T": "Yup, that's the big question."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Arataki Itto",
                    "T": "Gotta be honest, I have no idea."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Ushi",
                    "T": "Moo... Moo!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Arataki Itto",
                    "T": "Oh c'mon! Don't get mad at me, I'm just being real here."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Arataki Itto",
                    "T": "I did think about just using my oni super strength to dig our way out, but the rocks here are even tougher than prison walls..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Arataki Itto",
                    "T": "The rocks didn't even budge when Ushi charged 'em. It's pretty obvious this place is meant to keep us in here."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Arataki Itto",
                    "T": "The only thing I can do now is... well, take care of this exhausted little Lavender Melon."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Ushi",
                    "T": "Moo, moo! Moo."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Arataki Itto",
                    "T": "Yeah, I know... You're helping too, Ushi."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "I won't disturb you."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Arataki Itto",
                    "T": "Sure, you do you. Just remember, even if the sky comes crashing down, I'll prop it up with my own two hands! And don't worry, I'll take care of the little Lavender Melon."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
    "102921": {
        "Desc": "Talk to everyone",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Yanfei",
                    "T": "You haven't slept at all, are you sure you're okay? This place seems even more perilous than we first thought."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Yelan",
                    "T": "Don't worry about me. Staying focused under pressure for as long as it takes is my specialty."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Yelan",
                    "T": "Now, if I'm not mistaken, looks like you've got some new ideas."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Yanfei",
                    "T": "Hehe, how could you tell?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Yelan",
                    "T": "It's my job to keep tabs on people."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Yanfei",
                    "T": "I figured as much. They're just preliminary ideas at this point, but I haven't completely thought them through yet. I'll tell you more once my ideas have taken shape."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Yelan",
                    "T": "Sure, sounds good."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Yelan",
                    "T": "I also have some ideas of my own. I'll fill you in after I've confirmed some things."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Seems like a productive conversation."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Yelan",
                    "T": "Hehe, you think so?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Yanfei",
                    "T": "As they say, two heads are always better than one."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
