    "103019": {
        "Desc": "Talk to Xiao",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Xiao",
                    "T": "Ugh! ...*cough*"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Xiao",
                    "T": "Enough... phantom, be gone!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Bosacius",
                    "T": "Argh!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Xiao, are you okay?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "You haven't even recovered from your injuries yet..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Xiao",
                    "T": "This is my purpose. Don't worry about me."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Yelan",
                    "T": "So your invisible opponent was the legendary Bosacius, Marshal Vritras?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Xiao",
                    "T": "Yes."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Xiao",
                    "T": "So excuse my stubbornness. Bosacius has been missing for centuries... This may have been the last time I will ever see him."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "He was saying something about holding the line at all costs..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Xiao",
                    "T": "He fought here. The nameless yaksha from the legends... it was him."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "But didn't you say he'd always announce his name? How could his name be lost to time? ...What happened?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Xiao",
                    "T": "..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Xiao",
                    "T": "I don't know. Maybe he forgot who he was."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Yanfei",
                    "T": "Because the karma you spoke of drove him to madness?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Xiao",
                    "T": "Bosacius had already gone mad before he disappeared. There was no way of knowing if his memories were intact."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Yelan",
                    "T": "He still took part in the battle of The Chasm, despite having gone mad?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Xiao",
                    "T": "We yakshas are not a race that thrive in peacetime. It's likely that he was drawn by the scent of bloody war."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Xiao",
                    "T": "Slaughter is what we do best... Maybe it's the only thing we know."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Xiao",
                    "T": "This battle confirmed my suspicions. As we had speculated, this space reflects information from people's minds."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Xiao",
                    "T": "In other words, despite going mad, Bosacius came here. The illusion we saw just now is the impression he left behind."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Xiao",
                    "T": "This space recreated him as he was during the battle. The way he fought was so self-destructive... He couldn't possibly have survived."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "He fought the monsters..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Yelan",
                    "T": "Bosacius's illusion said he'd discovered the monsters' weakness and lured them underground."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Yelan",
                    "T": "What kind of place could this be? Defeating Khaenri'ah's monsters is no small feat, that's for sure."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Yanfei",
                    "T": "Guys, it could just be me, but... I think I'm suddenly feeling more tired than I was."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Yelan",
                    "T": "This space is really starting to affect us."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Xiao",
                    "T": "I believe Bosacius stayed here, underground. But now he is gone, and only his illusion remains."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Xiao",
                    "T": "If we don't leave, we may meet the same fate."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Let's go."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Xiao",
                    "T": "Time to move on."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Xiao",
                    "T": "You fought well, Bosacius. Goodbye."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
