    "103026": {
        "Desc": "Talk to everyone",
        "Step": "After encountering a series of space-and-time anomalies, you and the others manage to find some clues. You exchange information with one another in hopes of finding a way out.",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Huh? What's that shiny round thing on the ground?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "(It looks like...)"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Yanfei",
                    "T": "...The Fantastic Compass?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Yelan",
                    "T": "In the other spaces, the Fantastic Compass was always partially buried in the ground. But this one is lying flat, intact... as if somebody left it here."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "#Oh... {F#he}{M#she} was just a figment of your imagination, {NICKNAME}...?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "#So {F#he}{M#she} appeared as an illusion because you miss {F#him}{M#her} so much, huh?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "#I can sense that {F#he}{M#she} is not here."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "But at least we found this."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Mmm..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Yelan",
                    "T": "Yanfei, are you sure this is the Fantastic Compass you're looking for?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Yanfei",
                    "T": "I think so. There were no pictures in the will, but based on the description, it seems to check out."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Yanfei",
                    "T": "Yelan? What is it?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Yelan",
                    "T": "From the design and build, this Fantastic Compass looks extremely similar to the catalysts used by my clan. I just need to do this, and..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Yelan",
                    "T": "...Hmph, someone's used this before. There may be a hidden message inside."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Yelan",
                    "T": "Let's get out of here and find somewhere safer."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
